data.description: This beautiful 1 story home is nestled in the highly desirable Gruenefield subdivision.  Minutes away from Gruene Hall, Creekside Shopping, HEB and Canyon Lake...the conveniences of life are only a short distance away. This lovely home offers an Open Floor Plan with lots of upgrades.  You'll enjoy family gatherings around the kitchen island or even running over to Gruene for a nice evening.  This beautiful home offers 10 foot ceilings with 8 foot doors throughout, ceiling fans in all bedrooms as well as the living room and over the covered patio, updated LED light fixtures throughout and cabinet under-mounted lights in the kitchen, beautiful quartz countertops with an oversized kitchen island, Water Softener system is owned by the homeowner and will convey, extended backyard patio with lanai as well as a sprinkler system.
